==Finnish==

===Possessive suffix===
'''-ni''' (''suffixed to the (strong) vowel stem; the final <b>-n</b> of the case suffix or the <b>-t</b> of the plural is omitted'')

# first person singular possessive suffix.
#: ''kirjani'' "my book/books"
#: ''valaani'' "of my oath/to my oath" (&lt;''[[vala#Finnish|vala]]'')  '''or''' "my whale/whales" (&lt;''[[valas]]'')

